ed widespread praise from critics.</p><p> In a four-star review of the film, NME wrote: “The script contains unexpected subtlety, particularly during the tender moments which pack an emotional punch.</p><p> “Presumably, part of Mattel&#39;s motive for bringing Barbie to the big screen was changing her outdated image of rigid beauty ideals and unrealistic body conformism. So sprinkled throughout are marketing messages (“Barbie means you can be anything”) that sound like they come straight from a press release. Gerwig is clever enough to deliver these with self-awareness and some sarcastic jokes (Mirren thanking Barbie for ending misogyny is a highlight), meaning the balance between reality and commercial is never lost.对于一部表面上是为了宣传娃娃而存在的电影来说，这是值得称赞的。”</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/margot-robbie-once-faked-her-own-death-to-scare-a-babysitter-3471649">Margot Robbie once faked her own death to scare a babysitter</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
摩擦游戏可以让你从制作恐怖游戏中抽出时间https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/frictional-games-to-take-time-off-from-making-horror-games-3471605?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=frictional-games-to-take-time-off-from-making-horror-gamesImogen Donovan Fri, 21 Jul 2023 14:09:15 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPCPS4PS5 https://www.nme.com/?p=3471605 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/frictional-games-horror-games-stopping.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/frictional-games-horror-games-stopping.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/frictional-games-horror-games-stopping-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/frictional-games-horror-games-stopping-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/frictional-games-horror-games-stopping-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/frictional-games-horror-games-stopping-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/frictional-games-horror-games-stopping-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我相信这些游戏仍然会让人感觉像是摩擦游戏”</p><p>后<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/frictional-games-to-take-time-off-from-making-horror-games-3471605">摩擦游戏从制作恐怖游戏中抽出时间</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/frictional-games-horror-games-stopping.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/frictional-games-horror-games-stopping.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/frictional-games-horror-games-stopping-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/frictional-games-horror-games-stopping-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/frictional-games-horror-games-stopping-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/frictional-games-horror-games-stopping-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/frictional-games-horror-games-stopping-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>以<em>《半影》</em>和<em>《失忆症》</em>系列而闻名的瑞典开发商<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/frictional-games">Frictional Games</a>分享了其在未来游戏中淡化恐怖元素的意图。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/sounds-scary-why-horror-game-music-is-the-key-to-unlocking-true-fear-3079713">听起来很可怕：为什么恐怖游戏音乐是解锁真正恐惧的关键</a></strong></li></ul><p>在接受采访时，创意总监 Thomas Grip 解释说，情感投入是 Frictional Games 游戏中最重要的方面，而不是恐惧因素（来自<a href="https://80.lv/articles/frictional-games-on-its-history-developing-horror-games/">80lv</a> ）。 “虽然我们所有的游戏在某种程度上都是恐怖的，但我们真正想做的是获得一种‘可玩的沉浸感’，”他说。 </p><figure id="attachment_3447459" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3447459" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3447459" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Amnesia-The-Bunker.jpg" alt="失忆症：地堡" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Amnesia-The-Bunker.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Amnesia-The-Bunker-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Amnesia-The-Bunker-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Amnesia-The-Bunker-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Amnesia-The-Bunker-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Amnesia-The-Bunker-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3447459" class="wp-caption-text">失忆症：地堡。图片来源：摩擦游戏</figcaption></figure><p>谈到<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/amnesia-rebirth-is-free-next-week-on-the-epic-games-store-3205766">《失忆症：重生</a></em>》的母性主题和<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/soma"><em>SOMA</em></a>关于我们如何定义人类的哲学问题，Grip 赞扬了团队为平衡这些复杂主题以及有趣和恐怖的体验而做出的“整体”努力。</p><p> “我们在恐怖背景下传达了这些主题，但这些故事可以用另一种类型来讲述，”创意总监继续说道。 “对于未来的项目，我认为我们会减少一些恐怖方面的内容，以便更多地关注其他情感品质。”</p><p> “我相信这些游戏仍然会让人感觉像是摩擦游戏。我认为，沉浸感、个人旅程和整体视野是摩擦游戏的定义特征，而不仅仅是恐怖游戏本身，”他总结道。</p><p> Frictional Games 最近发布了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/amnesia-the-bunker-trailer-reveals-semi-open-world-ww1-horror-3359772"><em>《失忆症：碉堡》</em></a> ，以第一次世界大战为背景。主角亨利·克莱门特 (Henri Clément) 是一名被怪物困住的士兵，怪物会对玩家在试图逃脱死亡时做出的选择做出反应。据说<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/frictional-is-working-on-a-soma-style-game-alongside-amnesia-the-bunker-3398413">它的下一个标题</a>是一部“更大”的科幻恐怖片，专注于“像你在<em>《SOMA》</em>中看到的那种哲学东西”。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/assassins-creed-syndicate"><em>《刺客信条：枭雄》的</em></a>配音演员维多利亚·阿特金<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/assassins-creed-voice-actor-describes-ai-as-an-invisible-enemy-3471042">表达了她对在 mod 中使用人工智能来模拟演员声音的担忧</a>。</p><p>后<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/frictional-games-to-take-time-off-from-making-horror-games-3471605">摩擦游戏从制作恐怖游戏中抽出时间</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
